Because the right hand side of eq.() does not vanish,
current  is not a conserved current in the new
coordinate system , or in the new coordinate
system, the continuity equation does not hold. The reason
is simple: the transformation matrices eqs.( - )
or new coordiantes  carry some dynamics. The space-time
itself carries some dynamics, the physical vacuum of a physical
system is not a conserved system, so the physical system alone
is not a conserved system. The unite system of physical vacuum
and physical system is a conserved system. 


